query:
SELECT r.*, e.id as emp_id, e.name as emp_name, e.branchId as emp_branch
FROM employee_requests r
LEFT JOIN employees e ON r.employeeId = e.id
WHERE r.requestType = 'leave' AND r.status = 'approved'
ORDER BY r.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 10;
